title: Skrillex- Complete Discography 2007-2013 Organized into 21 Album
description:
This is a FULL collection of Sonny Moore's work over the years ever since he was known as "Sonny".

The following collection contains 1.64 GB (200 songs)in pure MP3s organized into 21 very clear albums/folders. These folders organize all of his released (320bit) albums, un-released songs, released singles, remixes, rips, live rips,mashups, miscellaneous etc. 

Thank you for leaving a comment if you're happy with this full discography!
